First field:
 apt-cache search mp3 | awk '{print $1}'


Last field:
 apt-cache search mp3 | awk '{print $NF}'

Everything except first column:
 awk '{ for (i=2; i<=NF; i++) printf "%s ", $i; printf "\n"; }'


